Interface Conditions

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConditionsTypes, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Service

    ConditionsStub

    public interface Conditions
extends com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Service, ConditionsTypes
    The Conditions interface provides methods to retrieve conditions related to a particular Supervisor. This interface was added in vSphere API 8.0.0.1.
